{"tid":851602,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"你知唔知你其實真係煮得好難食","createTime":"2018-10-07T09:27:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T13:45:45.000Z","uid":57308,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b91dc88e38c073ab5608c652878312fc5d40016e","tid":851602,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T09:27:02.000Z","msg":"係咁問問問，我咪答你煮得都ok唔差啊，咁答你又唔鍾意黑鳩我面<br />\n係咪要我呃鳩你話好撚好食啊你先滿意<br />\n又話唔鍾意人地呃你，想對你真誠啲<br />\n你想我點撚樣啊<br />\n你自己都試左味，好唔好食你心裡面冇數咩<br />\n我話飽你都要係咁逼我食<br />\n大佬我知係你一番心機<br />\n但真係好撚難食啊屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個飯甜到仆街，想點撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呻完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌"},{"pid":"c400465bc9b74ebaea0dcd8b520fb4485ac3d889","tid":851602,"uid":191246,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T09:27:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b1d1fca3e847c73848927f5cd0247295ef3b4c2","tid":851602,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c400465bc9b74ebaea0dcd8b520fb4485ac3d889","tid":851602,"uid":191246,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T09:27:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T09:35:06.000Z","msg":"下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"496ec65ba376968bc51d8b5236d6ab3f59a016c3","tid":851602,"uid":75373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T10:54:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd0971ccc82c7c5f13e90682f6f50d6ec37bd0a3","tid":851602,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,